title: Cowboys' CeeDee Lamb clears up rumors about why he, teammate were benched vs Raiders
text: Dallas Cowboys star CeeDee Lamb cleared up the reasons why he and George Pickens were benched for the team's first drive against the Las Vegas Raiders.
